        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一-介绍">一、介绍</h2>
<ul>
<li>还在羡慕 Discord 和 Telegram 的机器人么，还在为需要魔法才能使用而头疼么，现在，基于 Forge和 Fabric 的群服连接机器人来了。</li>
<li>此模组区别于插件版的群服连接，不想折腾插件的服主可以试试。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="二-提示">二、提示</h2>
<p>该模组不止一个教程，本教程适用于<a href="https://link.mcmod.cn/target/aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL0xhZ3JhbmdlRGV2L0xhZ3JhbmdlLkNvcmU=">Lagrange</a>协议端，若您在寻找其他协议端的教程，您可以略过本教程。</p>
<h2 id="三-准备工作">三、准备工作</h2>
<ul>
<li>一个QQ账户（建议使用价值不大的小号）</li>
<li>适用与您的设备的<a href="https://github.com/LagrangeDev/Lagrange.Core/releases">Lagrange版本</a></li>
<li>适用于您的Minecraft版本的<a href="https://github.com/Nova-Committee/McBot/releases">模组文件</a></li>
</ul>
<details class="wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow" open="" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin: 0px;"><summary style="box-sizing: inherit; cursor: pointer;">展开版本选择提示<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></summary><figure class="wp-block-table" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; box-sizing: inherit; display: block; overflow-x: auto;"><table class="has-fixed-layout" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 1px 0px 0px 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.1); border-image: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; table-layout: fixed; width: 660.241px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><tr style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); border-image: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: normal; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; word-break: break-word;">Lagrange.Core的选择：</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); border-image: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: normal; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; word-break: break-word;">模组文件的选择</td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); border-image: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: normal; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; word-break: break-word;"><code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">x64</strong></code>:基于<code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">x86_64</code>架构（即通常的64位<code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">Intel</code>或<code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">AMD</code>处理器）<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">arm64</strong></code>:<span>&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">ARM64</code>架构<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">arm</strong></code>: 32位<code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">ARM</code>架构<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">普通Linux环境</strong>：选择不包含<code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">musl</code>的版本<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">musl</strong>: 基于<code style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">musl</code>的Linux系统（例如Alpine Linux）</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); border-image: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: normal; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; word-break: break-word;">此处从略，请根据模组加载器和游戏版本选择<br style="box-sizing: inherit;">（<strong style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><kbd style="box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: Inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; hyphens: none;">提别提示：如果从releases获取到的版本出现明显bug，这很可能不是你的原因，请获取修正后的版本</kbd></strong>）</td></tr></tbody></table></figure></details>
<h2 id="四-教程开始">四、教程开始</h2>
<h3 id="1配置lagrange">1.配置Lagrange</h3>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Windows</th>
<th>Linux/MacOS</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>双击 Lagrange.OneBot.exe 运行即可</td>
<td>依次运行以下指令： <code>chmod +x ./Lagrange.OneBot</code> <code>./Lagrange.OneBot</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>第一次运行时, 会在同级目录下自动生成默认的 <code>appsettings.json</code> 配置文件, 你需要正确修改配置文件以设置 Lagrange</p>
<p>在配置文件按需修改后（推荐使用扫码登录）, 在命令行中按任意键, Lagrange 将正式运行在同一文件夹下会出现一张登录二维码图片 qr-0.png, 在二维码过期前尽快使用手机 QQ 扫码连接</p>
